    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 3rd level, you master the art of the ambush. You can give yourself a bonus to your initiative rolls equal to your Wisdom modifier.</p><p>At the start of your first turn of each combat, your walking speed increases by 10 feet, which lasts until the end of that turn. If you take the @action[Attack] action on that turn, you can make one additional weapon attack as part of that action. If that attack hits, the target takes an extra [[/damage 1d8]] damage of the weapon's damage type.</p></div>",
